.vscode/**
.vscode-test/**
.git/**
src/**
.gitignore
.yarnrc
vsc-extension-quickstart.md
**/tsconfig.json
**/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo
**/.eslintrc.json
**/.eslintrc.cjs
**/.gitignore
**/*.map
**/*.ts
**/*.d.ts
**/*.d.ts.map
*.vsix
*.tgz
../../**
# All sibling workspace packages — the bundled engine is copied into
# engine/ (no ../) inside this package via build:copy-engine, and any
# other sibling (sc-link-audio shipping as separate GPL-2.0-or-later
# artifact under Epic #187, plus future packages like midi-engine) is
# not part of the .vsix. .vscodeignore patterns match the literal
# relative path string vsce emits, so the previous `../engine/**`
# entry was per-package by accident — generalizing it to `../*/**`
# avoids needing a new exception every time a sibling package is added.
../*/**
engine/package-lock.json
engine/package.json
# Keep built engine, SuperCollider files, and runtime dependencies
!engine/dist/**
!engine/supercollider/**
!engine/node_modules/**
# Keep bundled scsynth (binary + plugins + libsndfile + LICENSE/NOTICE)
!engine/scsynth/**
# Keep legal templates (used by extract-scsynth-bundle.sh)
!legal/**
